{
  "description": "A nighttime cityscape featuring a vibrant fireworks display over a body of water. A long bridge with illuminated lights stretches across the water, leading towards a skyline of tall buildings. The buildings are lit with numerous lights, creating a dazzling urban panorama. The fireworks explode in a variety of colors \u2013 reds, greens, and whites \u2013 creating a spectacular burst of light against the dark sky. The foreground shows dark water, and in the distance, more lights indicate the continuation of the city. The composition is a wide-angle shot capturing the breadth of the urban landscape and the excitement of the pyrotechnics.",
